isLoading\" /></code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>수치 사용 지양 <br/>\n<span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 5px;font-size:13px;border-radius:3px;color:#B1380B;background:#ffded2;\">Bad</span> <code class=\"language-text\">p-[20px]</code> <br />\n<span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 5px;font-size:13px;border-radius:3px;color:#3D7317;background:#d2e9c1;\">Good</span> <code class=\"language-text\">size=\"lg\"</code></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"designmd\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#designmd\" aria-label=\"designmd permalink\" class=\"link-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Design.md</h2>\n<h2 id=\"ux-writing\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#ux-writing\" aria-label=\"ux writing permalink\" class=\"link-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>UX Writing</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrapper\"><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">상태</th>\n<th align=\"left\"> </th>\n<th align=\"left\"> </th>\n<th align=\"left\"> </th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><strong>Status</strong></td>\n<td align=\"